  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Newspaper announcement</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1911</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">On November 16th, 1911, the ‘Hotel Pariz’ grand cinema theatre announces screenings of the historical feature film, ‘Život i dela besmrtnog vožda Karadjordja’ (Life and deeds of the immortal leader Karadjordje), on November 17th, 18th, 19th and 20th, each day at 3 p.m. and 9 p.m.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The announcement was published in the newspaper ‘Novo vreme’ (New era) in Serbian Cyrillic. The ‘Hotel Pariz’ cinema was located in Belgrade. The dates were written according to the Julian calendar. November 16th, 1911, corresponds to November 28th of the Gregorian calendar and not to November 29th as indicated in the announcement’s subtitle.</ab>
